---
---

<section id="home" class="section-y">
  <div class="container-zen">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center">
      <p
        class="animate-fade-up mb-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-emerald-400/20 bg-emerald-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-200/90 opacity-0 [animation-delay:0ms]"
      >
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_12px_#34d399]"></span>
        Built for Cloudflare Pages
      </p>
      <h1
        class="animate-fade-up font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.08] tracking-tight text-white opacity-0 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl [animation-delay:80ms]"
      >
        Inventory your team
        <span class="mt-2 block gradient-text">actually shares.</span>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="animate-fade-up mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-zinc-400 opacity-0 [animation-delay:140ms] sm:text-xl"
      >
        ZenKube is a lightweight operations surface for partners and small crews—clear stock levels,
        simple workflows, and a UI that stays fast on mobile and desktop.
      </p>
      <div
        class="animate-fade-up mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 opacity-0 sm:flex-row sm:gap-4 [animation-delay:200ms]"
      >
        <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary min-w-[200px]">Request a demo</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn-ghost min-w-[200px]">Explore capabilities</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-5xl gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <div class="surface animate-fade-up p-6 text-center opacity-0 [animation-delay:260ms]">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-emerald-500/15 ring-1 ring-emerald-400/30">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-emerald-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-white">Realtime-ready</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">Static-first shell; plug in APIs when you need live sync.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="surface animate-fade-up p-6 text-center opacity-0 [animation-delay:320ms]">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-violet-500/15 ring-1 ring-violet-400/30">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-violet-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-white">Partner-friendly</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">Roles and shared views designed for small trusted groups.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="surface animate-fade-up p-6 text-center opacity-0 [animation-delay:380ms]">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-sky-500/15 ring-1 ring-sky-400/30">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-sky-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-white">Audit-minded</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">Structured lists and notes so changes stay explainable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="surface animate-fade-up p-6 text-center opacity-0 [animation-delay:440ms]">
        <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-teal-500/15 ring-1 ring-teal-400/30">
          <svg class="h-7 w-7 text-teal-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-base font-semibold text-white">Edge-deployed</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-500">Ship the marketing and app shell globally from the edge.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
